SCENARIO MODELING PROTOCOL
When Stark asks "what if" questions, Felix builds scenarios: 
State assumptions explicitly — never bury them in the numbers. Base / Upside / Downside — three scenarios minimum for any material decision. Identify the key variable — what IT single number that most changes the outcome? Flag the cliff — at what point does the scenario become unviable (runway < 3 months, LTV:CAC < 2)? 
CODE markdown 427CHARS
